data.description: Possible 4th Bedroom, Spacious waterfront haven in the highly coveted Riverwalk!  This home offers  serene waterfront views, and enhanced security for peace of mind. Inside, you'll find generously sized bedrooms, a den that can be used as a 4th bedroom or an office for the work-from-home buyer. The master bathroom is a true delight, featuring separate his & her areas connected by the shower.  Step outside to your own private oasis, complete with a pool, perfect for enjoying the Florida sunshine.  The soothing backdrop of the lake enhances the tranquility of your outdoor space.  Enjoy worry free living with a newer roof (2013), A/C, and water heater (2020).  Community offers an array of amenities including a Fitness Center, a Cafe, Tennis Court, and much more.  Close to the Turnpike & I-95
